headline: Costco’s DEI Commitment And Digital Push Weighed Against Premium Valuation
summary: Costco Wholesale has reaffirmed its diversity, equity, and inclusion programs while facing political and legal scrutiny in the US. The company has rolled out meaningful wage increases for frontline employees, reportedly ahead of many retail peers. Costco is accelerating digital efforts, including digital wallets and AI supported inventory tools, with strong traction in e-commerce channels. headline: Invesco’s SPHQ ETF Smoked The S&P 500 With A Simple Screen
summary: When most investors think about S&P 500 exposure, they picture owning the entire market. But what if you could filter that universe down to only the most financially sound companies? That’s the promise behind Invesco S&P 500 Quality ETF (NYSEARCA:SPHQ), a fund that screens for profitability, stability, and operational excellence rather than simply tracking market ...
